# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Environment Variables — Book Discovery App
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# VERCEL DEPLOYMENT
# -----------------
# Set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY in your Vercel project settings:
#   Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#
# This key is used server-side by the Vercel Edge Function at
# /api/worldview-audit.  It is NEVER exposed to the browser.
#
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Server-side only — used by api/worldview-audit.ts (Edge Function)
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT
# -----------------
# For local dev, run `vercel dev` (not `npm run dev`) so that
# the Edge Functions are served alongside the Vite frontend.
#
# Install the Vercel CLI: npm i -g vercel
# Link your project:      vercel link
# Start dev server:       vercel dev
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Optional: direct client-side key for local testing only
# (Do NOT set this in production — the edge function handles it)
VITE_CLAUDE_API_KEY=
